parameters.description:
Specify the name of the destination S3 bucket you want to write to.

The full path will be constructed out of
s3a://#{Destination S3 Bucket}/#{Destination S3 Path}

Specify the path within the destination bucket where you want to write to.

The full path will be constructed out of
s3a://#{Destination S3 Bucket}/#{Destination S3 Path}
